      "type": "intro",
      "html": "<style>\n@keyframes fadeInDown { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(-30px);} to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);} }\n@keyframes fadeInUp   { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(30px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);} }\n@keyframes pulse      { 0%,100%{ transform:scale(1);} 50%{ transform:scale(1.05);} }\n@keyframes shimmer    { 0%{ background-position:200% center;} 100%{ background-position:-200% center;} }\n.intro-wrap { display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; height:calc(100vh - 80px); background:#1a1a2e; text-align:center; padding:20px 40px; box-sizing:border-box; overflow:hidden; }\n.intro-badge { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#667eea,#764ba2); color:white; padding:5px 16px; border-radius:50px; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase; animation:fadeInDown 0.8s ease both; margin-bottom:12px; }\n.intro-title { font-size:clamp(20px,3.5vw,46px); font-weight:900; color:white; line-height:1.15; animation:fadeInDown 0.9s ease 0.2s both; margin-bottom:8px; }\n.intro-title span { background:linear-gradient(90deg,#f6a67e,#ff6b6b,#f6a67e); background-size:200% auto; -webkit-background-clip:text; -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent; animation:shimmer 3s linear infinite; }\n.intro-subtitle { font-size:clamp(12px,1.8vw,18px); color:#ffffffaa; animation:fadeInDown 1s ease 0.4s both; margin-bottom:4px; }\n.intro-author { font-size:13px; color:#ffffff66; animation:fadeInDown 1s ease 0.5s both; margin-bottom:20px; }\n.intro-cards { display:flex; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:center; animation:fadeInUp 1s ease 0.6s both; margin-bottom:20px; }\n.intro-card { background:#ffffff12; border:1px solid #ffffff22; border-radius:14px; padding:12px 18px; min-width:130px; max-width:170px; }\n.intro-card .icon { font-size:24px; margin-bottom:6px; }\n.intro-card .label { color:#ffffffcc; font-size:12px; line-height:1.3; }\n.intro-btn { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f6a67e,#ff6b6b); color:white; border:none; padding:14px 40px; border-radius:50px; font-size:17px; font-weight:700; cursor:pointer; animation:fadeInUp 1s ease 0.8s both, pulse 2s ease 2s infinite; box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(246,166,126,0.4); font-family:Rubik,sans-serif; }\n.intro-btn:hover { transform:scale(1.05); box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(246,166,126,0.6); }\n</style>\n<div class=\"intro-wrap\">\n  <div class=\"intro-badge\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"white\" style=\"margin-left:5px;vertical-align:middle;\"><polygon points=\"13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2\"/></svg> חינמי. פרטי. עובד אופליין.</div>\n  <div class=\"intro-title\">יש לכם הקלטה בעברית?<br><span>Vibe הופכת אותה לטקסט</span></div>\n  <div class=\"intro-subtitle\">קובץ וידאו, קובץ שמע, הקלטת פגישה, סרטון יוטיוב.<br>כל תוכן מדובר בעברית הופך לטקסט תוך דקות.<br>בחינם. על המחשב שלכם.</div>\n  <div class=\"intro-author\">עומר טייכר · מדריך וטכנאי מחשבים</div>\n  <div class=\"intro-cards\">\n    <div class=\"intro-card\"><div class=\"icon\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f6a67e\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polygon points=\"23 7 16 12 23 17 23 7\"/><rect x=\"1\" y=\"5\" width=\"15\" height=\"14\" rx=\"2\"/></svg></div><div class=\"label\">וידאו, אודיו, כל פורמט</div></div>\n    <div class=\"intro-card\"><div class=\"icon\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f6a67e\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/><line x1=\"2\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"22\" y2=\"12\"/><path d=\"M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 014 10 15.3 15.3 0 01-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 01-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 014-10z\"/></svg></div><div class=\"label\">עברית, אנגלית ועוד מגוון שפות</div></div>\n    <div class=\"intro-card\"><div class=\"icon\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f6a67e\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"11\" width=\"18\" height=\"11\" rx=\"2\"/><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0110 0v4\"/></svg></div><div class=\"label\">הכל נשאר אצלכם. לא עולה לאינטרנט</div></div>\n  </div>\n  <button class=\"intro-btn\" onclick=\"nextSlide(1)\">▶&nbsp;&nbsp;בואו נתחיל</button>\n</div>"
